    "Experiments Related Companies SelectionHere, we use Toyota as an example to illustrate the analysis and results.",
    "First, we used NER to extract the organization names from Toyota news.",
    "Table 1 shows the top ten entity names in Toyota news.",
    "Then we selected only companies from the entity names, such as Tesla, Ford, and GM.",
    "Due to the limitation of the API we used to collect the news data, only publicly listed companies are chosen from the entity names."
